skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: birthstone quiz
des: Play an interesting game of quiz with Alexa. While playing the quiz, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next question. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the quiz. this quizzes you about modern and traditional gemstones and which month they corresponded with.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
